org.eclipse.draw2d
Interface SchemeBorder.SCHEMES

Enclosing class:
SchemeBorder
public static interface SchemeBorder.SCHEMES

Interface which defines some commonly used schemes for the border. These schemes can be given as input to the SchemeBorder to generate appropriate borders.
